## Summary

This change improves mobile navigation across the Bouquet Hospitality OS by increasing touch targets, extracting reusable mobile tab components, adding GSAP-driven sidebar animations, and ensuring WCAG 2.2 compliance.

**Execution order:** Sidebar foundation → Tab navigation → GSAP animation → Accessibility audit.

